{
  "id": "diary-travel",
  "name": "旅行日记",
  "category": "diary",
  "description": "一本充满冒险气息的旅行日记，记录旅途中的见闻和感受",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.04,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "旅行|冒险|探险|旅途|异国",
        "description": "旅行相关场景可能触发"
      },
      {
        "type": "event",
        "operator": "after",
        "value": "travel",
        "description": "旅行事件后可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "location": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "当前位置/目的地"
    },
    "date": {
      "type": "date",
      "format": "YYYY年MM月DD日",
      "description": "日记日期"
    },
    "dayCount": {
      "type": "number",
      "description": "旅行天数"
    },
    "weather": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "天气图标"
    },
    "title": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日记标题"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 500,
      "description": "日记正文内容"
    },
    "photoDescription": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "照片描述"
    },
    "photoCaption": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "照片说明"
    },
    "moodIcons": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "心情图标组合"
    },
    "footer": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "日记结尾"
    },
    "stampIcon": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "✈️",
      "description": "邮票装饰图标"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一篇旅行日记的内容。\n\n背景信息：\n- 写日记的人：{{author}}\n- 当前地点：{{location}}\n- 旅行天数：{{dayCount}}\n- 天气：{{weather}}\n- 旅途见闻：{{experience}}\n\n要求：\n1. 内容要充满对旅途的热爱和好奇\n2. 描述当地的风土人情或美景\n3. 语气要轻松愉快，有冒险精神\n4. 字数控制在200-400字之间\n5. 可以提及想拍的照片\n\n请直接输出日记内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "adventure",
    "colors": ["#87ceeb", "#98d8c8", "#f7dc6f"],
    "mood": "轻松愉快"
  },
  "rarity": "uncommon",
  "collectible": true
}